MAYER STEEL PIPE April Sales Fall 22.12% (Table) : 2020 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-05-10T09:05:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-10/mayer-steel-pipe-april-sales-fall-22-12-table-2020-tt.html
MAYER STEEL PIPE said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 22.12% to NT$431,949,000 from NT$554,669,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2011           4/2010
Sales            431,949          554,669    
YOY%             -22.12%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,954,764        1,894,997   
YOY%              3.15%  
=================================================================
 